ávo EÚ </span> </a> <span class="dropdown_arrow">▼</span> <ul class="dropdown-menu child-menu" role="menu"> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_116" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_116" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;vyhladavanie-v-prave-eu" role="menuitem">Vyhľadávanie v práve EÚ</a> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_117" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_117" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;pripomienkovanie-prava-eu" role="menuitem">Pripomienkovanie práva EÚ</a> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_119" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_119" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;vyhladavanie-v-procesoch-eu" role="menuitem">Vyhľadávanie v procesoch EÚ</a> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_120" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_120" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;vyhladavanie-navrhov-aktov-eu" role="menuitem">Vyhľadávanie návrhov aktov EÚ</a> </li> </ul> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item dropdown" id="layout_68" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_68" aria-haspopup='true' class="dropdown-toggle" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;sudne-rozhodnutia" role="menuitem"> <span> Súdne rozhodnutia </span> </a> <span class="dropdown_arrow">▼</span> <ul class="dropdown-menu child-menu" role="menu"> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_72" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_72" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;judikaty" role="menuitem">Judikáty</a> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_73" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_73" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;vseobecne-sudy-sr" role="menuitem">Všeobecné súdy SR</a> </li> <li class="lfr-nav-item" id="layout_74" role="presentation"> <a aria-labelledby="layout_74" href="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;www&#x2e;slov-lex&#x2e;sk&#x2f;europsky